ize: 14pt\">黄凌翔，分管科研、实验室建设、城镇化与新农村平台建设、社会服务；联系实验室、公共管理系。</span><span style=\"font-family: 楷体;font-size: 14pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"p0\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, 宋体, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; padding: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 1.8em; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><span style=\"font-family: 楷体;font-size: 14pt\">副</span><span style=\"font-family: 楷体;font-size: 14pt\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: 楷体;font-size: 14pt\">院</span><span style=\"font-family: 楷体;font-size: 14pt\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: 楷体;font-size: 14pt\">长：</span><span style=\"font-family: 楷体;font-size: 14pt\">王振坡，分管学科建设、研究生教育、学位点建设、国际交流；联系城市与区域经济研究所。</span></p><p style=\"font-family: \" microsoft=\"\" margin-top:=\"\" margin-bottom:=\"\" padding:=\"\" font-size:=\"\" line-height:=\"\" white-space:=\"\" text-align:=\"\" background-color:=\"\"><br /></p>', '', null, null, null, '0', '0', '1970-01-01', '1469774291');
